nt/uploads/2008/06/macosx.jpg\">maÅ¡ini</a> :)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>ocena:</strong> sedi 5<br />\r\n<strong>minus:</strong> pogreÅ¡al uporabo DocBlock-a v PHP kodi oziroma psevdokodi pri podanih primerih<br />\r\n<strong>Å¾elje:</strong> Å¡e veÄ podobnih dogodkov v prihodnje, interaktivne delavnice<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLahko samo reÄem Å¡e PHP konferenca je uspela in Happy blogging(coding)!','Zgodila se je prva slovenska PHP konferenca',0,'','publish','open','open','','zgodila-se-je-prva-slovenska-php-konferenca','','http://phpkonferenca.si/o-konferenci/\nhttp://hasin.wordpress.com/2008/01/05/once-upon-a-time-there-was-smarty/','2008-07-09 12:59:03','2008-07-09 10:59:03','',0,'http://www.internet-solutions.si/?p=75',0,'post','',0),(76,1,'2008-07-08 07:54:10','2008-07-08 05:54:10','','Zatopljen v predavanja ...',0,'Zatopljen v predavanja ...','inherit','open','open','','me_php_konferenca','','','2008-07-08 07:54:10','2008-07-08 05:54:10','',75,'http://www.internet-solutions.si/wp-content/uploads/2008/07/me_php_konferenca.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(77,1,'2008-08-13 15:46:18','2008-08-13 13:46:18','<strong>Sponzorirana spletna stran: <a href=\"http://www.icarusdown.net/\">The Burning Water Project by Icarus Down</a></strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a rel=\"lightbox\" href=\'http://www.internet-solutions.si/wp-content/uploads/2008/08/the-burning-water-project-by-icarus-down.png\'><img align=\"right\" style=\"padding:5px;\" src=\"http://www.internet-solutions.si/wp-content/uploads/2008/08/the-burning-water-project-by-icarus-down-150x150.png\" alt=\"The Burning Water Project By Icarus Down\" title=\"The Burning Water Project By Icarus Down\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"size-thumbnail wp-image-78\" /></a>Stripped down to the dry humming of the strings or ampped up to an oscillation of a voltage form the analog / acoustic and the digital / electronic collide together in an Icarus Down project as two sides of a double album.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>an